$ Registry: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Nls\Language

sa:

  → Windows/development/Internationalization/language[Windows: languages]

  The four digit hexadecimal values under this registry key can apparently be mapped to a two character keyboard layout name
  with the registry key
  → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/System/CurrentControlSet/Control/Keyboard-Layout/DosKeybCodes[`HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Keyboard Layout\DosKeybCodes`].

